	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Okay, after digging through some old threads I figured out how to remove the Sprite 0 check (as well as disable the status bar). I now have a copy of SMB that has
<br />1. No sound engine
<br />2. No status bar
<br />
<br />Can you guys think of any other code that could be removed / simplified to make porting easier?
<br />
<br />Also, I have a bunch of NOPs scattered throughout and even more .byte $ff, [...] at the end of the code. Is there a way to automatically pad the rom to a certain size?
<br />
<br />Any help would be awesome, thanks!

		

		</td>
	</tr>
