	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I'm thinking about changing strategies. To cut costs I would use a lower resolution screen, something closer to Gameboy Color resolution.
<br />
<br />Is it going to be very difficult to modify SMB to run at a lower / different aspect ratio resolution? It looks like I can modify GetScreenPosition to be 160px wide rather than 256.

		

		</td>
