	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Change the camera logic to center on the area to the right of Mario within the first 256 pixels?  That would give you limited backwards scrolling, and would still handle almost like a fully wide screen.  You could just use a "second camera", run the game logic against the first camera, but run the drawing logic against the second camera.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


